                                    <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12" />
                                </svg>
                            </span>
                            <div class="feature-text">
                                <h5>Lens Quality</h5>
                                <p>Crystal-clear optics with advanced coatings for optimal vision</p>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <span class="feature-check">
                                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                                    <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12" />
                                </svg>
                            </span>
                            <div class="feature-text">
                                <h5>Frame Durability</h5>
                                <p>Built to last with premium materials and expert craftsmanship</p>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <span class="feature-check">
                                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                                    <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12" />
                                </svg>
                            </span>
                            <div class="feature-text">
                                <h5>Personalized Fit</h5>
                                <p>Custom adjustments to ensure perfect comfort all day long</p>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <span class="feature-check">
                                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                                    <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12" />
                                </svg>
                            </span>
                            <div class="feature-text">
                                <h5>Quality Workmanship</h5>
                                <p>Meticulous attention to detail in every frame we create</p>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <a href="/Products/Index" class="btn-view-all">View All</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Dynamic Brand Selector -->
            <div class="dynamic-brand-selector">
                <div class="dbs-header">
                    <h3 class="dbs-title">Browse by Brand</h3>
                    <div class="dbs-toggle">
                        <button id="btn-frames" class="dbs-btn active" onclick="switchBrandTab('frames')">Frame Brands</button>
                        <button id="btn-lenses" class="dbs-btn inactive" onclick="switchBrandTab('lenses')">Lens Brands</button>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="dbs-container">
                    <div id="list-frames" class="dbs-list fade-in">
                        <!-- JS handles population -->
                    </div>
                    <div id="list-lenses" class="dbs-list hidden">
                        <!-- JS handles population -->
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Scoped Styles for Dynamic Brand Selector -->
    <style>
        .dynamic-brand-selector {
            margin-top: 4rem;
            padding-top: 2rem;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .dbs-header {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
        }

        @@media (min-width: 768px) {
            .dbs-header {
                flex-direction: row;
                align-items: center;
                justify-content: space-between;
            }
        }

        .dbs-title {
            font-size: 1.875rem; /* 30px */
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #111827;
            margin: 0;
            letter-spacing: -0.025em;
        }

        .dbs-toggle {
            display: inline-flex;
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            padding: 0.25rem;
            border-radius: 9999px;
            align-self: flex-start;
        }

        @@media (min-width: 768px) {
            .dbs-toggle {
                align-self: auto;
            }
        }

        .dbs-btn {
            padding: 0.625rem 1.75rem;
            border-radius: 9999px;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
            border: none;
            outline: none;
        }

        .dbs-btn.active {
            background-color: #004d40;
            color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 2px 4px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
        }

        .dbs-btn.inactive {
            background-color: transparent;
            color: #4b5563;
        }

        .dbs-btn.inactive:hover {
            color: #111827;
            background-color: #e5e7eb;
        }

        .dbs-container {
            position: relative;
            min-height: 100px;
            overflow: hidden;
            width: 100%;
            padding-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .dbs-list {
            display: flex;
            overflow-x: auto;
            gap: 1rem;
            -ms-overflow-style: none;
            scrollbar-width: none;
        }
        
        .dbs-list::-webkit-scrollbar {
            display: none;
        }

        @@media (min-width: 768px) {
            .dbs-list {
                flex-wrap: wrap;
                overflow-x: visible;
            }
        }

        .dbs-list.hidden {
            display: none;
        }

        /* The individual chip buttons */
        .brand-chip {
            white-space: nowrap;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 0.5rem; /* 8px */
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            color: #1f2937;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 1.125rem; /* 18px */
            transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
            background-color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0 1px 2px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            flex-shrink: 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .brand-chip:hover, .brand-chip:focus {
            border-color: #004d40;
            background-color: #f0fdfa; /* Light teal */
            color: #004d40;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 77, 64, 0.1), 0 2px 4px -1px rgba(0, 77, 64, 0.06);
            outline: none;
        }

        .brand-chip:active {
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
        
        @@media (min-width: 768px) {
            .brand-chip {
                flex-shrink: 1;
            }
        }

        /* Animations */
        .fade-in {
            animation: dbsFadeIn 0.35s ease-out forwards;
        }
        
        @@keyframes dbsFadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
    </style>

